        <p class="text-slate-700">ELSS opens specific TEER 4 and TEER 5 NOCs in the tourism, hospitality, food processing, and long-haul trucking sectors. The wage you can claim is bounded by the federal Job Bank prevailing wage for that NOC in your BC economic region.</p>
        <div class="overflow-x-auto">
          <table class="min-w-full text-sm border-collapse border border-slate-200">
